## MEDICAL DISCLAIMER

This software is provided for educational and research purposes only. It is 
NOT FDA-approved and should NOT be used for clinical decision-making without 
proper validation and regulatory approval.

Always verify AI-generated content against original clinical notes. The 
accuracy of AI-generated summaries should be validated by qualified healthcare 
professionals before use in clinical practice.

The authors and contributors assume no liability for any errors, omissions, or 
damages arising from the use of this software in clinical settings.

## HIPAA COMPLIANCE NOTICE

This software, as provided, is NOT HIPAA-compliant. Patient data is sent to 
third-party LLM providers (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google). 

DO NOT use with real patient data without:
1. Signing Business Associate Agreements (BAA) with LLM providers
2. Implementing proper encryption (in-transit and at-rest)
3. Adding audit logging
4. Implementing user authentication and authorization
5. Conducting security risk assessment
6. Implementing on-premises LLM alternatives

Users are solely responsible for ensuring compliance with HIPAA, GDPR, and 
other applicable data protection regulations.
